{"tid":1807124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蕭若元落區現身元旦大遊行：2020香港有希望","createTime":"2020-01-01T16:00:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T05:16:40.000Z","uid":184679,"like":22,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"146b7fdd45e3a37365f6270b72821a88e34fc88c","tid":1807124,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:00:35.000Z","msg":"雖然2020.01.01民陣元旦大遊行不歡而散，但今天較早時間蕭若元（燒山）則在現場出現，引發不少年輕人和中年Fans搶著要自拍，場面歡樂。燒山也相當親民，來者不拒。不少人一開始就祝燒山身體健康，其後有不少市民大叫「燒山好嘢」、「燈神好嘢」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.winandmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/stephen-shiu-at-admiralty.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2Fstephen-shiu-at-admiralty.jpg&h=698c226e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n燒山亦稱「大家辛苦了」，要繼續努力，稱香港2020年有希望。但搞笑地隨即被現場的人指「你應該話無希望呀嘛！」。有市民稱住天水圍，都專登去燒山餐廳支持燒山咁話。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.winandmac.com/2020/01/stephen-shiu-at-admiralty/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2F2020%2F01%2Fstephen-shiu-at-admiralty%2F&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOAIm5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=9ad6dbe6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.winandmac.com/2020/01/stephen-shiu-at-admiralty/</a>"},{"pid":"df235d3e9852bc6a1e8c9ab44f3aadc7221aa5ed","tid":1807124,"uid":230239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:01:46.000Z","msg":"燒山<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aff8913da09e72931403e0638c6211c49017d361","tid":1807124,"uid":8417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:02:04.000Z","msg":"[無懼打壓] 黑警打壓工會，我哋就要加入工會！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1807119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1807119</a>"},{"pid":"499457db3b805eecaf79bab6af69f58d70ac810f","tid":1807124,"uid":265192,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:03:19.000Z","msg":"被現場的人指「你應該話無希望呀嘛！」 <img src=\"/assets/faces/norm